data.description: Welcome Home!  This picture perfect Colonial offers the perfect combination of elegance, sophistication and charm. Enter through an inviting and spacious entrance foyer, living room, formal dining room, dining room, eat -in kitchen with center island and brand new full bath. The second floor offers four bedrooms, newly renovated full bath with a walk-up attic for additional storage or finish it for additional living space.  Enjoy your privacy in the beautiful yard with a paver patio, pergola and plenty of green space. Convenient distance to schools, train station and shopping. Just minutes from Route 4 and 20 minutes to the GWB.
